snippet.textDisplay:
One should not compare the great Mehdi Hassan saab's  rendition with this one.
Both are completely different compositions.
Credit should go firstly to Nisar Bazmi saab; what beautiful lyrics.
This song is beautifully composed and sung; by both in their own way.
Love the fact that while sticking to theme of fusion, the tabla got so much prominence in the song.
May Allah SWT bless every one who made this possible.
